Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}那些人幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}那就是學生會會長代理人…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}直井文人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}莊家滿貫！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}別搞得一團糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}我們需要天使
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}「Handsonic ver 2」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}要向神明反抗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}你讓我反省什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}你願意承認嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}就是他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}神啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}{\fs30}你的人生也是真實存在的啊！
